  You have just entered a value for a variable that is not correct.
  * if this is a typing error, you can double-click the entered value in the terminal to modify it,
  The entered value must be numeric and integer (because that is how the variable in which it will be stored has been defined).
  * run the algorithm again entering a value of the appropriate type,
  * or modify your algorithm, checking all the expressions and definitions in which this variable appears.

320
  One of the expressions on this line that uses the negation operator (NO/~) has an operand on its left. But the negation operator is unary and its only operand must be on the right.
  For example, in "No 5==x", the result "5==x" will be its operand; but in an expression like "a no b" there is an error, since either the "a" should not be there ("no b" is correct), or an operand is missing ("a y no b" is also correct).
  * Check whether there is an operand before the negation in the expression.
  * Remove the operand or add the missing operator.
  It may also happen that the problem is due to a misunderstanding of operator precedence.
  * If the expression is complex, add parentheses to the subexpressions to alter/make explicit the desired precedence.

321
  The expression "De Otro Modo" is used only within a multiple-selection structure (<A href="segun.html">Según</A>). You are using "De Otro Modo" inside another type of structure, or outside any structure.
  * Check the nesting of your data structures and the correct placement of their FinXXX terminators
  Note: This expression must be placed after the different options for the control variable, and indicates the path to follow when its value does not match any of the options. 

322
  You are trying to modify, through a read or assignment, the value of a variable that you should not modify. This is usually the case for the counter of a Para loop. Since the structure handles the counter automatically, the programmer should not modify it.
  * Check that you are not trying to read into or write to a variable that functions as the counter of a Para.
  * If your intention really was to modify the counter in order to alter how the Para works, you should consider replacing it with a different structure: Mientras or Repetir.

